author: Google
description:
The #DoodleForGoogle student art contest is open!

This year’s theme is “My superpower is…”  and we’re inviting U.S. K-12 students to celebrate their unique strengths and express them through original art — for a chance to win college scholarships, tech packages for their school, and have their artwork featured on google.com.

Submissions are now open until December 10 at doodle4google.com

Artwork by @yonk.online
title: Submissions for #DoodleForGoogle are now open until December 10.

author: Google

Submissions are now open until December 10 at doodle4google.com
title: YONK brings Doodle for Google to life
